<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TMaL12">
<l>namaṉumuṟ kalaṉum pēca narakilniṉ ṟārkaḷ kēṭka</l>
<l>narakamē cuvarkka mākum nāmaṅka ḷuṭaiya nampi</l>
<l>avaṉatū raraṅka meṉṉā tayarttuvīḻn taḷiya māntar</l>
<l>kavalaiyuṭ paṭukiṉ ṟāreṉ ṟataṉukkē kavalkiṉ ṟēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Not saying</l>
<l rend="indent">‘Raṅgam’ is the town of Him, --</l>
<l rend="indent">the elite among men who has [such] names</l>
<l rend="indent">that hell itself became heaven</l>
<l rend="indent">as Yama and Mudgala spoke</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] as the people staying in hell heard [them]--</l>
<l>the wretched people are caught in affliction, forget [the truth], and fall.</l>
<l>Thinking [thus], I am troubled by that.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
